  "prompt": "How can I use my Jio 4G SIM ?",
  "response": "To use your Jio 4G SIM, follow these steps:\n\n1. Ensure compatibility:\n- Check if your mobile phone supports 4G/VoLTE\n- If not, you may need a 4G-enabled device\n\n2. Get your SIM activated:\n- Visit a Jio store\n- Provide necessary documents (ID proof, address proof)\n- Complete SIM activation process\n\n3. Insert the SIM:\n- Turn off your phone\n- Locate the SIM tray\n- Insert the Jio 4G SIM carefully\n- Restart your phone\n\n4. Configure network settings:\n- Go to phone settings\n- Select \"Mobile Networks\"\n- Enable 4G/LTE network mode\n- Select Jio as your preferred network\n\n5. Setup Jio apps:\n- Download MyJio app from Play Store/App Store\n- Create your account\n- Verify your number\n\n6. Activate data pack:\n- Use MyJio app or Jio website\n- Select suitable data plan\n- Recharge your account\n\n7. Start using services:\n- Make calls\n- Use mobile data\n- Access Jio apps and services\n\nRemember to keep your phone updated and maintain a good network signal for optimal performance.",
